## Chi Tiết Auto-Generated Files

```
PHASE 2 (Auto Generate) sinh ra:
├── .agent/
│   ├── 00_MASTER.md           ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT.yaml[project]
│   ├── 01_STRUCTURE.md        ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT.yaml[architecture]
│   ├── 02_TASK_LIST.md        ⬅️ 01_STRUCTURE.md
│   ├── 03_*_CONTRACT.md       ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT.yaml[contracts]
│   ├── 05_RULES_{LANG}.md     ⬅️ .skill/{lang}.md + INTERVIEW_OUTPUT
│   └── 06_BUILD_CONFIG.md     ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT.yaml[technology]
│
├── .skill/
│   └── {lang}.md              ⬅️ _shared.md + INTERVIEW_OUTPUT[technology]
│
├── .test/
│   └── scenarios/T{n}_*.md    ⬅️ 02_TASK_LIST.md + 01_STRUCTURE.md
│
├── .map/
│   ├── current/component_tree.yaml  ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT[architecture]
│   ├── current/data_flow.mmd        ⬅️ INTERVIEW_OUTPUT[architecture]
│   └── refs/ (empty, ready)          ⬅️ Created
│
├── .doc/
│   └── PROGRESS.md            ⬅️ 02_TASK_LIST.md
│
├── .agent/STATE.md            ⬅️ phase: planning
│
└── .token/coding/INIT.yaml    ⬅️ Log generation tokens
```

## .bug/ Được Tạo Sau Khi Code Xong (PHASE 4)

```
PHASE 4 (Bug Scan) tạo .bug/:
└── .bug/
    ├── 01_SCAN_LOG.md         ⬅️ Kết quả scan từ .map/, .doc/, src/
    └── 02_BUG_LIST.md         ⬅️ Bugs phát hiện được (auto-gen template)
```

## Chi Tiết Coding Phase

```
PHASE 3 (Coding) - Mỗi task:
Input:
  • .agent/02_TASK_LIST.md[T{n}]
  • .agent/05_RULES_{LANG}.md
  • .skill/{lang}.md
  • .test/scenarios/T{n}.md
  
Output:
  • Code file
  • .map/current/ (nếu component mới)
  • .doc/PROGRESS.md (status update)
  • .token/coding/T{n}.yaml (token log)
```

## Chi Tiết Bugfix Phase

```
PHASE 5 (Bugfix) - Mỗi bug:
Input:
  • .bug/02_BUG_LIST.md[BUG-{id}]
  • Code cần fix
  
Output:
  • .sim/dry_run_{id}.md
  • Fixed code
  • .map/diff/v{X}_to_v{Y}.yaml
  • .map/refs/BUG-{id}.yaml
  • Updated .bug/02_BUG_LIST.md
  • .token/bugfix/BUG-{id}.yaml
```

